A Kyrie Irving for Ben Simmons swap is very ‘possible’, per Nick Wright.

Nets would receive one of the best defenders in the league alongside two of the best scorers in James Harden and Kevin Durant.

Kyrie Irving would accumulate the scoring that the Sixers desperately desire. The trio of Kyrie/Embiid/Harris could go places.

Who wins a Kyrie-Simmons exchange?
